<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her pfleger, als ir uns
                                                  <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> aber
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt
                                                von Wernher Newmeyrs wegen, das
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>, und dancken
                                                  <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit
                                                  <expan>fleissiklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sölchs
                                                guten willen, als ir gen uns habt. Und also wöllen
                                                  <add>wir</add>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit darauff
                                                  <expan>antwurtte<ex>n</ex></expan> bey unserselbs
                                                  <add>poten</add>, die wir darümb czu euch
                                                  <expan>schike<ex>n</ex></expan> wollen.
                                                  <expan>Dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo wir
                                                  <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit lieb und
                                                dinste beweisen möhten etc.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi
                                                  <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>do<ex>min</ex>icam</expan> invocavit.</ab>
